<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="189">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="189">
China: Jiangxi and Hunan provinces (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 9" captionStartId="F9" captionText="Figure 9. Records of Haplodrassus yinae sp. nov., Hitobia xiaoxi sp. nov., and Zelotes dingnan sp. nov. from Jiangxi Province, China" figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1108.85655.figure9" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/705990" pageId="0" pageNumber="189">9</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
